<br>
Load Annul Magic and Debuff him! get rid of his pesky Sow and AC buffs and hit him with that big ol' two hander of yours. I know most people on a blue server don't use golem wands, but get one or two and spend two-three clicks on him <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Thats 12 buffs down the drain right away <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
once he is debuffed it is just a matter of running around and hitting him with your 2hs till he stops moving <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  If you have Two handed Bash AA skill then try and encourage him to cast! it takes up alot of his melee time and Bash rules in PvP.<br>
<br>
I can't think up a senario where he wins unless you go LD and he kills you then. Good luck!  <p><A href=http://pub86.ezboard.com/bbringersofretribution><IMG src="http://www.everquestsin.netfirms.com/images/nevydarkerbringer.jpg"> </A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiustus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iustus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Holy Defender</span><br>  Posts: 639<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/3/02 1:26:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=81.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Duel 60 Pal vs. 60 ranga with epic</span><hr size=1> If you catch him using trueshot, and you sure he used it, just use Divine Aura and med while taunting him profusely. (This works on manaburning wizards too, but is a lot harder to pull off because they can duck their cast - so wont work on the same guy twice).<br>
<br>
Shield of the immaculate cancels the slow off ranger epic.<br>
<br>
